cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper presents a deep learning approach for estimation of the bead parameters in welding tasks, which involves computer vision (CV) and machine learning (ML) techniques. Therefore, cs.CV and cs.LG are the most likely categories. The use of a neural network architecture also suggests the possibility of the paper belonging to cs.NE. The estimation of the bead parameters in welding tasks involves robotics (RO) and artificial intelligence (AI) techniques, which further supports the inclusion of these categories.
